This first serie named "THE" is dedicated to rework of photographs representing in a clear or abstract manner the objects to which they relied..

Photography is one of my favorite medium, I'm usually using it as a way to abstract an idea of the real, abstract a vision of an object.

I hope sincerely that you will appreciate it.
